SAFETY NOTICE
-------------
This course teaches defensive and authorized security testing skills. All
hands-on activities are designed to run ONLY inside the college's isolated
NetLab teaching environment against instructor-provided practice systems.
Nothing in this material authorizes testing against systems you do not own
or lack explicit written permission to assess. Adopters are responsible for
providing a contained lab environment and for communicating applicable law
and acceptable-use policy to learners.
